OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FInterfaith group set to    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fclose after funding stopped
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A British charity set up nearly 40     
OL,6, years ago to improve understanding     
OL,7, between faith groups is set to close on
OL,8, Thursday after the government cut off  
OL,9, funding.                               
OL,11,FLast month, Communities Secretary      
OL,12,FMichael Gove said he was "minded to    
OL,13,Fwithdraw" funding for the Inter Faith  
OL,14,FNetwork (IFN) after the appointment of 
OL,15,FHassan Joudi, a former deputy secretary
OL,16,Fgeneral of the Muslim Council of       
OL,17,FBritain (MCB), as a trustee.           
OL,20,FMr Joudi has not commented on the      
OL,21,Fgovernment's decision.                 
